    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>03 July 1947</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 439</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-6c9db3aa-faf6-4403-99d6-6f817fe03d18'>
            
<p class="">9.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b">
                Mr. Sparks
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-07-03/debates/0eb62218-2c51-470d-bea7-f720926e8167/Hospitals(VoluntaryEfforts)#contribution-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Minister of Health if he is aware that for many years voluntary bodies have organised fêtes, bazaars and sales of work, etc., for the benefit of voluntary hospitals; and, in view of the passing of these hospitals to State responsibility next year, whether he will state his policy with regard to the continuance of such voluntary effort for the particular benefit of local hospitals.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-07-03/debates/0eb62218-2c51-470d-bea7-f720926e8167/Hospitals(VoluntaryEfforts)#contribution-be83de3a-9efd-4d17-96a5-00a85aafe02b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e">
                Mr. Bevan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-07-03/debates/0eb62218-2c51-470d-bea7-f720926e8167/Hospitals(VoluntaryEfforts)#contribution-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">When the new hospital service comes into being, the various new governing bodies will have full power to receive and hold voluntary funds from any source, independently. It must be <span id="1479" class="column-number" data-column-number="1479"></span> understood, however, that no charge may be made on patients for any part of the service, except for those specifically mentioned in the Act or regulations.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-07-03/debates/0eb62218-2c51-470d-bea7-f720926e8167/Hospitals(VoluntaryEfforts)#contribution-dd62fc36-fa7e-4e41-a19d-cbf1060c028e">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-6ec47aa1-a45f-40d5-8b2b-990eb20e3a4e">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-6ec47aa1-a45f-40d5-8b2b-990eb20e3a4e">
