    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-301415d9-4490-4fc5-92e2-218a8a615aef">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-301415d9-4490-4fc5-92e2-218a8a615aef">
                Mr. Bevan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-301415d9-4490-4fc5-92e2-218a8a615aef" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-07-03/debates/0eb62218-2c51-470d-bea7-f720926e8167/Hospitals(VoluntaryEfforts)#contribution-301415d9-4490-4fc5-92e2-218a8a615aef">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Each of the hospitals can raise funds for additional purposes, such as welfare, and things of that sort, but the main body of revenue will come from the State. It must be quite clear that no charge can be made to a patient, because the service is free.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-301415d9-4490-4fc5-92e2-218a8a615aef" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-07-03/debates/0eb62218-2c51-470d-bea7-f720926e8167/Hospitals(VoluntaryEfforts)#contribution-301415d9-4490-4fc5-92e2-218a8a615aef">
